% =====================================================
% STRESS TEST: %%ENSEMBLE directive
% 8 voices | offsets -8 to +15 | jitter changes per section
% tempo 108 -> 88 -> 120
% PNEUMA + ENSEMBLE combined on multiple voices
% Minimalism x Dub x Gamelan
