% --- SECTION B: GAMELAN BLOOM (bars 17-32) ---
% Jitter opens to 4, kotekan fully interlocking, gamelan density
% --- SECTION C: DUB BREAKDOWN (bars 33-48) ---
% Tempo drops to 88, jitter opens to 8, space IS the instrument
% --- SECTION D: PHASE CLIMAX (bars 49-64) ---
% Tempo 120, max density, all 8 voices at full offset spread
